name: Eco Minded Solutions
overview: Eco Minded Solutions is a San Diego-based landscape design company that offers green, environmental friendly landscaping and hardscaping construction for residential and commercial properties. We offer comprehensive landscape design, construction, and maintenance services to clients seeking to improve the beauty and function of their properties. Aside from creating and implementing water saving landscapes and enhancement features that rely on solar energy, we are committed to providing our clients with a cost effective plan and excellence in customer service. As a fully licensed, bonded, and insured landscape company in San Diego, the team at Eco Minded Solutions can execute your landscape renovation with the professionalism and reliability you deserve.
